<title>Unit test: programlisting.014</title>

<para>This tests the parameters for trimming leading and trailing blank lines
from a verbatim environment.</para>

<para>Defaults (trim trailing, not leading):</para>

<programlisting>


line four of four


</programlisting>

<para>Trim trailing, not leading, explicitly:</para>

<programlisting><?db verbatim-trim-leading='false' verbatim-trim-trailing='true'?>


line four of four


</programlisting>

<para>Trim leading, not trailing:</para>

<programlisting><?db verbatim-trim-leading='true' verbatim-trim-trailing='false'?>


line one of four


</programlisting>

<para>Trim both:</para>

<programlisting><?db verbatim-trim-leading='true' verbatim-trim-trailing='true'?>


line one of one


</programlisting>

</article>
